F_{r}=12\frac{U_{0}}{R_{0}}\left[\left(\frac{R_{0}}{R_{0}+x}\right)^{13}-\left(\frac{R_{0}}{R_{0}+x}\right)^{7}\right]
(\frac{1}{R_{0}+x})^{13}
(\frac{1}{R_{0}+x})^7
F_{r}\approx -\left(\frac{72U_{0}}{R_{0}^{2}}\right)x
R_{0}
\left| \frac{x}{R_{0}}\right|<1
=\frac{1}{R^{13}_{0}}\left(1+(\frac{x}{R_{0}})\right)^{-13}\approx \frac{1}{R^{13}_{0}}\left(1+(-13)\frac{x}{R_{0}}\right)=\frac{1}{R^{13}_{0}}\left(1-13\frac{x}{R_{0}}\right)
\frac{1}{R^{13}_{0}}.\frac{1}{1+(\frac{x}{R_{0}})^{13}}
F_{r}\approx -\left(\frac{72U_{0}}{R_{0}^{2}}\right)x=12\frac{U_{0}}{R_{0}}\left[\frac{1}{R^{13}_{0}}\left(1-13\frac{x}{R_{0}}\right)-\frac{1}{R^{7}_{0}}\left(1-7\frac{x}{R_{0}}\right)\right]
\frac{x}{R_0}
\frac{1}{R_0^{13}}
\frac{1}{R_0^7}
\left(\frac{R_0}{R_0 + x}\right)^{13} = \left(1+\frac{x}{R_0}\right)^{-13} = 1 - 13\frac{x}{R_0} + \mathcal{O}\left(\frac{x^2}{R_0^2}\right)
\left(\frac{R_0}{R_0 + x}\right)^7 = \left(1+\frac{x}{R_0}\right)^{-7} = 1 - 7\frac{x}{R_0} + \mathcal{O}\left(\frac{x^2}{R_0^2}\right)
\left(\frac{R_0}{R_0 + x}\right)^{13}-\left(\frac{R_0}{R_0 + x}\right)^7 = -6\frac{x}{R_0} + \mathcal{O}\left(\frac{x^2}{R_0^2}\right)
F_r \approx \frac{12U_0}{R_0}\left[-6\frac{x}{R_0}\right] = -\frac{72U_0}{R_0^2}x
